{
  "page": "Orkmont",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Iron_Islands.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/bd/Iron_Islands.jpg/350px-Iron_Islands.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/bd/Iron_Islands.jpg/525px-Iron_Islands.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/bd/Iron_Islands.jpg/700px-Iron_Islands.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Iron_Islands.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Orkmont among the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Orkmont</b> is one of the islands that make up the island chain called the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>. Orkmont is centrally located, with <a href=\"/index.php/Blacktyde\" title=\"Blacktyde\">Blacktyde</a> to the north, <a href=\"/index.php/Harlaw\" title=\"Harlaw\">Harlaw</a> to the southeast, <a href=\"/index.php/Pyke_(island)\" title=\"Pyke (island)\">Pyke</a> to the south, and <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a> to the west.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Economy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Economy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Houses\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Houses</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Economy\">Economy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orkmont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Economy\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Orkmont.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e4/Orkmont.jpg/350px-Orkmont.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"250\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e4/Orkmont.jpg/525px-Orkmont.jpg 1.5x, /images/e/e4/Orkmont.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Orkmont.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Orkmont by Franz Miklis © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Rugged and mountainous, Orkmont is rich in ore, including <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lead\" title=\"Lead\">lead</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Tin\" title=\"Tin\">tin</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It was once covered in forest but the timber was used extensively for shipbuilding.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Orkmont is larger and richer than <a href=\"/index.php/Pyke_(island)\" title=\"Pyke (island)\">Pyke</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_greyjoys_of_pyke.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_greyjoys_of_pyke.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Houses\">Houses</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orkmont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Houses\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Orkmont contains the seats of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Orkwood\" title=\"House Orkwood\">House Orkwood</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tawney\" title=\"House Tawney\">House Tawney</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> The island also has a branch of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Orkmont\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Orkmont\">House Goodbrother</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> The extinct houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\">Greyiron</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">Hoare</a>, both of whom once ruled the Iron Islands as <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_king\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Iron king\">iron kings</a>, came from Orkmont.<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orkmont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Urras_Greyiron\" title=\"Urras Greyiron\">Urras Greyiron</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_king\" title=\"Salt king\">salt king</a> of Orkmont, was crowned the first <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a> in a <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot\" title=\"Kingsmoot\">kingsmoot</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Longships from Orkmont attacked the western shores of the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Harrag_Hoare\" title=\"Harrag Hoare\">Harrag Hoare</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Urron_Greyiron\" title=\"Urron Greyiron\">Urron Greyiron</a>, a salt king from Orkmont, slaughtered his rivals at a kingsmoot on Old Wyk, becoming the first hereditary <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Orkwood\" title=\"House Orkwood\">House Orkwood</a> of Orkmont helped to overthrow <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\">House Greyiron</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_iron_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_iron_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> During the rule of the iron kings of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a>, merchants and traders from Orkmont were known to call at <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Following the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Harren_Hoare\" title=\"Harren Hoare\">Harren Hoare</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_Rivers\" title=\"King of the Isles and the Rivers\">King of the Isles and the Rivers</a>, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Burning of Harrenhal\">burning of Harrenhal</a>, an ironman of Orkmont declared himself king<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreignof_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreignof_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup> but was killed in the <a href=\"/index.php/Invasion_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Invasion of the Iron Islands\">succession squabble</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_greyjoys_of_pyke.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_greyjoys_of_pyke.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During <a href=\"/index.php/Greyjoy%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Greyjoy&#39;s Rebellion\">Greyjoy's Rebellion</a>, the forces of King <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a> conquered Orkmont.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_old_way_and_the_new.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orkmont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orkmont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Jake_Murray_Raiders_of_Orkmont.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/86/Jake_Murray_Raiders_of_Orkmont.jpg/350px-Jake_Murray_Raiders_of_Orkmont.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"280\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/86/Jake_Murray_Raiders_of_Orkmont.jpg/525px-Jake_Murray_Raiders_of_Orkmont.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/86/Jake_Murray_Raiders_of_Orkmont.jpg/700px-Jake_Murray_Raiders_of_Orkmont.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Jake_Murray_Raiders_of_Orkmont.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Raiders of Orkmont by Jake Murray © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Orkwood\" title=\"Alyn Orkwood\">Alyn Orkwood</a> of Orkmont supports <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a> with twenty longships.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> Besides the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Orkwood\" title=\"House Orkwood\">Orkwoods</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother_of_Orkmont\" title=\"House Goodbrother of Orkmont\">Goodbrothers</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tawney\" title=\"House Tawney\">Tawneys</a> also travel from Orkmont to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot_on_Old_Wyk\" title=\"Kingsmoot on Old Wyk\">kingsmoot on Old Wyk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orkmont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The name of Orkmont may be inspired by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Orkney\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Orkney\">Orkney</a>, an archipelago in the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northern_Isles\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Northern Isles\">Northern Isles</a> of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scotland\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Scotland\">Scotland</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-14\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orkmont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Map_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Map of the Iron Islands\">Map of the Iron Islands</a></i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: The Black Blood.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_greyjoys_of_pyke.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_greyjoys_of_pyke.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_greyjoys_of_pyke.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: The Greyjoys of Pyke.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A St